    </section>

    <!-- ── How It Works ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="how-section" id="how-it-works">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-tag">Simple process</div>
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Four steps and your family's prescription is paid and ready — from anywhere in the world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-row">
            <div class="journey-track"></div>

            <div class="journey-step">
                <div class="journey-badge">1</div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-icon">📄</div>
                    <h4>Send the Prescription</h4>
                    <div class="journey-tags">
                        <span class="journey-tag">💊 Pharmacy</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Upload the prescription and your relative's contact details through our secure portal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="journey-step">
                <div class="journey-badge">2</div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-icon">🧾</div>
                    <h4>Pharmacy Confirms the Bill</h4>
                    <div class="journey-tags">
                        <span class="journey-tag">✅ Itemized Bill</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>A verified pharmacy in Côte d'Ivoire reviews the prescription and confirms the exact XOF amount.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="journey-step">
                <div class="journey-badge">3</div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-icon">💳</div>
                    <h4>Pay Securely in USD</h4>
                    <div class="journey-tags">
                        <span class="journey-tag">🔒 Secure Stripe Payment</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Pay online in seconds using any card — the pharmacy receives the equivalent in XOF.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="journey-step">
                <div class="journey-badge">4</div>
                <div class="journey-card">
                    <div class="journey-icon">🏥</div>
                    <h4>Family Collects the Medication</h4>
                    <div class="journey-tags">
                        <span class="journey-tag"><svg class="ci-flag ci-flag-xs" viewBox="0 0 3 2" aria-label="Côte d'Ivoire"><rect width="1" height="2" fill="#F77F00"/><rect x="1" width="1" height="2" fill="#fff"/><rect x="2" width="1" height="2" fill="#009A44"/></svg> Trusted Local Partners</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>DiaspoDirect pays the pharmacy directly. Your relative collects their medication — no cash handling, no waiting.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="steps-cta">
            <a href="/Account/Register" class="btn-primary-cta">Start a Request</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Pharmacy Network ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="network-section" id="network">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-tag">Our network</div>
            <h2>Pharmacy Partners in Côte d'Ivoire</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">We work with licensed, verified pharmacies across Côte d'Ivoire so your family always has a trusted place to collect their medication.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="network-grid">
            <div class="network-card">
                <div class="network-icon-wrap">
                    <svg class="network-svg-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z"/>
                        <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h4>Abidjan &amp; Beyond</h4>
                <p>Partner pharmacies in Cocody, Plateau, Yopougon, Marcory, and other neighborhoods — growing nationwide.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="network-card">
                <div class="network-icon-wrap">
                    <svg class="network-svg-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="4" y="2" width="16" height="20" rx="2"/>
                        <path d="M8 7h8M8 11h8M8 15h5"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h4>Itemized Invoices</h4>
                <p>Every prescription comes with a detailed XOF bill. You know exactly what you're paying for before you confirm.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="network-card">
                <div class="network-icon-wrap">
                    <svg class="network-svg-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 2L3 7v5c0 5.25 3.75 10.15 9 11.35C17.25 22.15 21 17.25 21 12V7z"/>
                        <polyline points="9,12 11,14 15,10"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h4>Licensed &amp; Vetted</h4>
                <p>All pharmacy partners are licensed providers, verified by our team before joining the DiaspoDirect network.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="network-card">
                <div class="network-icon-wrap">
                    <svg class="network-svg-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/>
                        <path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h4>Notifications at Every Step</h4>
                <p>You and your family are notified when the prescription is received, billed, paid, and ready for pickup.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Services ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="services-section" id="services">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-tag">What we offer</div>
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Growing beyond pharmacy — see what's available today, and what's coming next.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <!-- Current -->
            <div class="services-col">
                <div class="services-col-label current">Available Today</div>
                <div class="service-card featured">
                    <div class="service-icon">💊</div>
                    <h3>Pharmacy Prescription Billing</h3>
                    <p>Send a prescription to a verified pharmacy in Côte d'Ivoire. Get the exact XOF bill, pay in USD via Stripe, and DiaspoDirect pays the pharmacie directly — your family just shows up to collect.</p>
                    <a href="/Account/Register" class="service-link">Send a prescription →</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Coming soon -->
            <div class="services-col">
                <div class="services-col-label soon">Coming Soon</div>
                <div class="coming-soon-cards">
                    <div class="service-card muted">
                        <div class="service-icon">🎓</div>
                        <h3>Education</h3>
                        <p>Pay school fees and tuition directly to your relative's school in Côte d'Ivoire.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card muted">
                        <div class="service-icon">💡</div>
                        <h3>Utilities</h3>
                        <p>Pay electricity and internet bills for your family — on time, every time.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card muted">
                        <div class="service-icon">🏥</div>
                        <h3>Healthcare &amp; Clinics</h3>
                        <p>Extend support beyond prescriptions to clinic visits, consultations, and lab work.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card muted">
                        <div class="service-icon">🚕</div>
                        <h3>Transportation</h3>
                        <p>Pay for transport fares and travel costs for your family back home — directly and securely.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card muted">
                        <div class="service-icon">💧</div>
                        <h3>Water Bills</h3>
                        <p>Cover water bills so your family's home never runs dry.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card muted">
                        <div class="service-icon">🏠</div>
                        <h3>Rent Payments</h3>
                        <p>Ensure your family's home is secure by paying rent directly to landlords back home.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Contact ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-tag">Get in touch</div>
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Have questions? We'd love to hear from you. Reach out to the DiaspoDirect team.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-grid">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">📧</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Email</h4>
                        <p>info&#64;diaspodirect.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">🏢</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Company</h4>
                        <p>Flaubert Group LLC<br />Texas, United States</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">🌍</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Service Area</h4>
                        <p>Côte d'Ivoire — expanding across Africa</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon">⏱️</div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>Response Time</h4>
                        <p>We respond within 1–2 business days.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <EditForm Model="contactModel" OnValidSubmit="HandleContactSubmit" FormName="contact" method="post" class="contact-form">
                <DataAnnotationsValidator />
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>First Name</label>
                        <InputText @bind-Value="contactModel.FirstName" placeholder="Jean" class="form-control" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Last Name</label>
                        <InputText @bind-Value="contactModel.LastName" placeholder="Kouassi" class="form-control" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Email Address</label>
                    <InputText @bind-Value="contactModel.Email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" class="form-control" />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Subject</label>
                    <InputText @bind-Value="contactModel.Subject" placeholder="Question about prescription payments" class="form-control" />
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Message</label>
                    <InputTextArea @bind-Value="contactModel.Message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us how we can help…" class="form-control" />
                </div>
                @if (contactSent)
                {
                    <div class="alert alert-success">Thanks! We'll get back to you within 1–2 business days.</div>
                }
                @if (contactError)
                {
                    <div class="alert alert-danger">Something went wrong. Please try again or email us directly.</div>
                }
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary-cta contact-submit" disabled="@contactSubmitting">
                    @(contactSubmitting ? "Sending…" : "Send Message")
                </button>
            </EditForm>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Why DiaspoDirect ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="why-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-tag">Why DiaspoDirect</div>
            <h2>Built for Trust</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Trust is critical when people are sending money for healthcare. Here's why families rely on us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-grid">
            <div class="why-item">
                <div class="why-icon">🔒</div>
                <h4>Bank-Grade Security</h4>
                <p>All payments processed through Stripe with full encryption and fraud protection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-item">
                <div class="why-icon">🤝</div>
                <h4>Trusted Pharmacy Partners</h4>
                <p>We work directly with verified pharmacies — your family collects, no middlemen.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-item">
                <div class="why-icon">📊</div>
                <h4>Transparent Pricing</h4>
                <p>See the exact CFA amount and small service fee before you pay — no surprises.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-item">
                <div class="why-icon">📱</div>
                <h4>Works on Any Device</h4>
                <p>Pay from your phone, tablet, or computer anywhere in the world — no app needed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── About Flaubert Group LLC ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="who-section" id="who-we-are">
        <div class="who-inner">
            <div class="who-text">
                <div class="section-tag">Our company</div>
                <h2>About Flaubert Group LLC</h2>
